                    .foregroundColor(.white)

                Text("çŠ¬å¥½ãã¨ãƒ¯ãƒ³ã¡ã‚ƒã‚“ã‚’ã¤ãªã’ã‚‹ã‚¢ãƒ—ãƒª")
                    .font(.subheadline)
                    .foregroundColor(.white.opacity(0.8))

                // ğŸ  çŠ¬ã‚’é£¼ã£ã¦ã„ã‚‹äººå‘ã‘ãƒœã‚¿ãƒ³
                NavigationLink(destination: OwnerRegistrationView(isRegistered: $isRegistered)) {
                    selectionButtonLabel(text: "çŠ¬ã‚’é£¼ã£ã¦ã„ã‚‹", color: Color.white.opacity(0.4), textColor: .white, icon: "house.fill")
